					type: "item"
					item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
					count: 2
				}
			]
		}
		{
			title: "Performance Fuels"
			icon: "gtceu:cetane_boosted_diesel_bucket"
			x: -1d
			y: 2d
			description: ["Cetane-Boosted Diesel adds cetane enhancers (a Chemical Reactor step) to standard diesel to raise its combustion rating, increasing EU output in combustion engines by roughly 25%. Gasoline, produced from cracked naphtha fractions through a separate pathway, powers different engine tiers and Gas Turbines. Both are significant upgrades over base diesel. Running cetane-boosted diesel in the Large Combustion Engine is the standard mid-game power strategy that carries cleanly into HV with no further refinery changes required."]
			dependencies: ["NC01000000000013"]
			id: "NC01000000000014"
			tasks: [
