		}
		{
			title: "The Nuclear Ladder"
			icon: "gtceu:nuclear_reactor"
			shape: "diamond"
			x: 4d
			y: 4d
			description: ["From a Chemical Reactor producing basic reagents to a closed nuclear fuel cycle processing plutonium and MOX rods, you have traversed the full chemistry and nuclear chain in GTCEu. Your oil refinery provides high-grade fuels for combustion power; your electrolyzers and centrifuges support circuit production and alloy synthesis; your reactor generates the EU needed to push into EV and beyond. The chemical industry is not a sidequest — it is the foundation on which all late-game GTCEu material production is built."]
			dependencies: ["NC01000000000021", "NC01000000000015"]
